Deployment pipeline: {
    style: {
        font-size: 40
        bold: true
    }
    shape: sequence_diagram

    Developer: Developer
    GitHub: GitHub Repository
    Actions: GitHub Actions
    GHCR: GitHub Container Registry (GHCR)
    Azure: Azure VM

    Developer -> GitHub: 1. Push Tag / Create Release
    GitHub -> Actions: 2. Trigger Release Workflow
    Actions -> Actions: 3. Build Docker images\n(webapp, users, game, gamey)
    Actions -> Actions: 4. Run tests (Vitest / cargo test)\n+ SonarCloud quality gate
    Actions -> GHCR: 5. Push images\n(ghcr.io/arquisoft/yovi_en2b-*)
    Actions -> Azure: 6. SSH: docker compose pull && up -d
    Azure -> GHCR: 7. Pull latest images
    Azure -> Azure: 8. Restart containers\n(zero-downtime where possible)
}